						<!-- Feature 1 -->
							<section class="container box feature1">
								<div class="row">
									<div class="12u">
										<header class="first major">
											<h2>Rich Science Accessible to All</h2>
											<p>The SMARTS Consortium operates four 1-meter class telecopes on Cerro Tololo. &nbsp;<a href="http://www.astro.yale.edu/smarts/about.htm">Membership in SMARTS</a>&nbsp;is open to individuals or institutions, including international partners.</p>
										</header>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="row">
									<div class="4u">
										<section>
											<a href="0.9m.html" class="image featured"><img src="images/ctio-0.9m.jpg" alt="" /></a>
												<h3>0.9-m + 2KCCD</h3>
												<p>A 13.5' x 13.5' imager with a variety of filters. Observing mode is traditional user runs.</p>
											</header>
										</section>
									</div>
									<div class="4u">
										<section>
											<a href="1.3m.html" class="image featured"><img src="images/ctio-1.3m.jpg" alt="" /></a>
												<h3>1.3-m + ANDICAM</h3>
												<p>Simultanious optical (6' x 6') and IR (2.5' x 3.5') imager. Observing preformed in queue and service mode.</p>
											</header>
										</section>
									</div>
									<div class="4u">
										<section>
											<a href="1.5m.html" class="image featured"><img src="images/ctio-1.5m.jpg" alt=""s/></a>
												<h3>1.5-m + CHIRON</h3>
												<p>High resolution spectrometer covering 410-870 nm. Observing preformed in queue and service mode.</p>
											</header>
										</section>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="row">
									<div class="12u">
										<p>The Yale 1-m telescope is also available to private users if sufficent number of nights can be sold to ensure financial viability. The telescope is currently equipped with a 20' x 20' 4K CCD. Potential partners who are interested in providing thier own instrument are encouraged to contact the SMARTS team.</p>
										<h1 class="icon fa-camera">  Photo-credit (left to right): Todd Henry, Fernando Cortez, CTIO</h1>
									</div>
								</div>
							</section>

